  "title": "Sales Coordinator (Freight forwarding) (Up to $3500 / Kallang)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Sales Coordinator (Freight forwarding) (ID4764)<br />Location : Kallang<br />Working Hour: Monday to Friday: 8.00am -5.00pm, Saturday :8.00am– 12.00pm (Alternate Sat Off)<br />Salary : $3200-$3500<br /><br />Sales Coordinator (Freight forwarding)<br />Responsibilities:<br />• Act as the main liaison for client communication<br />• Communicate and coordinate effectively with internal and external parties<br />• Handle and prepare shipping documents (e.g. Delivery Order, Bill of Lading, Arrival Notice, Tax Invoice, etc.)<br />• Perform customs import permit declarations<br />• Liaise and coordinate with overseas agents, customers, haulers, and warehouses to ensure smooth shipment delivery<br />• Serve as the main point of contact with sites, customers, and vendors to ensure smooth delivery operations<br /><br />Requirement<br />• Physically fit<br />• Must have Sales Coordinator (Freight forwarding) experience</p>",
